(1)Automation” ka matlab hai – kaam ko manually karne ki bajaye software ya system khud automatically kar de. 😎
SailPoint aur enterprise systems me ye bahut common hai, aur ye time save karta hai aur errors kam karta hai.

2️⃣ SailPoint me Automation ka matlab:-
Enterprise me, SailPoint ke developer ye kaam automate karte hain:
Manual Process	Automation in SailPoint
HR ko manually naye employee ke accounts create karna	SailPoint automatically Active Directory, Email, SAP accounts create kare
Manager se manual approval lena	Approval workflow automatically trigger ho jaye
Users ka access quarterly check karna	Reconciliation/Policy Enforcement automatically run ho jaye
Extra access detect karke remove karna	SailPoint automatically Deprovision kare